      "text": "\"Singleton\" - These must be thread safe. They are created and reused for EVERY usage of the thing.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Singleton\" - These must be thread safe. They are created and reused for EVERY usage of the thing.\n",
